      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ATTICA BLUE (6) shapes nicely here coming off a brilliant 19.54 win at Angle Park over 342m. Has the ability and expected to go close again. MANTIS BALE (4) ran good time (22.18) when second last start over 390m at this track, the second placing in a row. Expected to do much better this time. ELMA'S GIRL (7) chased the lead early from the inside and boxed on well to finish third, beaten 10 lengths (23.92) at Horsham in a Restricted WIN over 410m. Form from her last run is proving strong. Expected to feature. ADRENALINE BURST (8) flew the lids and led all the way last time. Sure to figure prominently.",
